    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know i should talk to a doctor but they are so expensive and it takes forever to get an appointment. plus i already know the sertraline is the problem. if i just stop the sertraline today and start the st johns wort tomorrow, would that be okay? i just want to get off the chemicals and try something cleaner without a huge transition period.",
